{"tid":850668,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(心靈脆弱者勿入) 本世紀最恐怖靈異照片","createTime":"2018-10-06T16:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T17:44:33.000Z","uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6734c9971e3c0c63e4cfb96047a0523bac4dd567","tid":850668,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/06/235901_b0ee65b0d795e667023cae70e174dedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F06%2F235901_b0ee65b0d795e667023cae70e174dedb.jpg&h=2860e14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我先來介紹一下：杜月笙情人孟小冬<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n也許你不知道她因何恐怖，她本來是一個大家閨秀。一個偶然的機會與杜月笙相遇，倆人情投意合。後來由於政局不穩，杜月笙也死於亂槍之下。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n這個可憐的女人在二樓上吊自殺，據說死相極為恐怖！ ！不久房子換了主人，可他們住的第一晚就出事了，周圍鄰居半夜傳出鬼一樣的號叫。令人毛骨悚然，等到第二天人們發現兩個人被開膛了。 。 。 。 。 。 。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n因此房子成為了一座鬼宅！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n後經過政府同意，房子被燒掉了。可奇怪的是她的一幅照片卻不時出現在上海灘！據說看見這幅照片的人家的主人全死了。至今在上海一些老人的聊天中也會提到這件事。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n我最後要說的是：凡是看到這張照片的人都有被找上的危險。但不要怕，如果回貼說(((老子什麼鬼都不信)))即可保平安。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/06/235852_b0ee65b0d795e667023cae70e174dedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F06%2F235852_b0ee65b0d795e667023cae70e174dedb.jpg&h=c4763d83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"059538ad680dc2aa6ae518a30520f1ed556865f1","tid":850668,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"老子什麼鬼也不怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6013cf228c86bccaa63da34d6bdbddd4eddbe3df","tid":850668,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"找數未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4b60a0aa6e3abcc3edc4766f0f91459e768344","tid":850668,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s